# Benchmark
benchmark/results/
benchmark/data/
benchmark/streaming-data/
benchmark/streaming-results/*
# Keep the curated reference CSVs + their README in version control. Local re-runs of the
# streaming-scalability benchmark write fresh CSVs alongside these — the negation only
# whitelists the four committed reference files, so new runs stay ignored.
!benchmark/streaming-results/README.md
!benchmark/streaming-results/streaming_E1_20260413_094028.csv
!benchmark/streaming-results/streaming_E2_20260413_091542.csv
!benchmark/streaming-results/streaming_E3_20260413_103456.csv
!benchmark/streaming-results/streaming_E4_20260413_103909.csv
benchmark/tools/